high_descs: Turn right go to the end of the sofa closer to the wall.
Pick up the tomato on the sofa further away from the cup.
Turn around and go to the middle of the sofa.
Place the tomato in the middle of the sofa
Pick up the knife from the sofa/
Slice the tomato on the sofa.
Take the knife to the section of the sofa closer to the doorway.
Slice the tomato on the sofa closer to the doorway.
Go back to the middle of the sofa.
Place the knife on the sofa behind the tomato in the middle
Pick up a slice of tomato from the middle of the sofa.
Turn around to the microwave.
Place the tomato slice in the microwave in the left corner.
Head back to the sofa, to the tomato closer to the doorway.
Pick up a slice of the tomato.
Turn around and head back to the microwave.
Place the tomato slice in the microwave behind the other slice.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of tomato from two different tomatoes in the microwave.

high_descs: Look down to the sofa just ahead of you, going towards its right end.
Pick up the tomato that is closer to the middle of the sofa.
Walk around to the other end of the sofa.
Place the tomato down on the seat of the sofa beside the one you picked the tomato up from.
Pick up the knife from the sofa seat you placed the tomato down on.
Slice the tomato you placed down.
With the knife in hand, approach the single seat right to the left of the sofa.
Slice the tomato that is on that seat.
Go right again to where you sliced the first tomato.
Place the knife down behind the tomato.
Pick up one slice of the tomato from the sofa.
Turn around and go to the microwave opposite the sofa.
Place the tomato slice inside the microwave.
Go back to the sofa, this time going to the single seat where you sliced the second tomato.
Pick up one slice from the tomato.
Go back to the microwave.
Place the second tomato slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Slice two tomatoes, pick up one slice from each and place them in a microwave.
